high_descs: Turn right, go forward a step, turn right, go forward to the table.
Take the spatula on the left from the table.
Turn left, go forward a step, turn left, go forward to the sink.
Wash the spatula in the sink then take it out.
Turn around, go forward to the table.
Put the spatula on the table to the right of the bowl and in front of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed spatula on a table.

high_descs: Make a right to walk to the kitchen island.
Pick up the spatula from the kitchen island.
Turn around to walk the sink.
Rinse the spatula in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Turn around to walk to the kitchen island.
Set the spatula down on the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a spatula to set on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn right and go past the fridge then turn right and go to the table
Pick up the spatula from the front of the head of lettuce on the table
Turn left then turn left again and go to the sink
Put the spatula in the sink and turn on the water, then turn off the water and take the spatula out of the sink
Turn right then turn right again and go back to the table
Put the spatula on the table to the right of the bowl
anns.task_desc: Put a washed spatula on a table
